@model List<VirtualPatDiagnosis.Models.ExamCase> 
@* 👆 這裡的 ExamCase 請換成你專案中對應的資料庫模型名稱 *@
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "選擇教案案例";
}

<style>
    .select-body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        background-color: #f4f7f6;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        font-family: 'Microsoft JhengHei', sans-serif;
    }
    .select-title {
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
    .card-container {
        display: flex;
        gap: 25px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        max-width: 80%;
    }
    .case-card {
        background: #ffffff;
        border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 30px;
        width: 320px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .case-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
        border-color: #3498db;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(52,152,219,0.15);
    }
    .case-title {
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #34495e;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .case-desc {
        color: #7f8c8d;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        display: -webkit-box;
        -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
        -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
        overflow: hidden; /* 避免敘述太長破壞排版 */
    }
    .enter-btn {
        background-color: #3498db;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        padding: 10px 25px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>

<div class="select-body">
    <h1 class="select-title">請選擇今日欲測驗的教案案例</h1>
    
    <div class="card-container">
        <!-- 核心動態化：從資料庫撈出幾筆，畫面上就自動顯示幾筆 -->
        @foreach (var item in Model)
        {
            <div class="case-card" onclick="location.href='/Read/ReadQuestion?caseId=@item.Id'">
                <div class="case-title">@item.Title</div>
                <div class="case-desc">@item.Description</div>
                <button class="enter-btn">開始讀題</button>
            </div>
        }
    </div>
</div>
